      <scopecontent id="aspace_602f6d85f43ad2cb7972b4d3770a1214">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consists of black and white photographs of the Yale Art and Architecture Building shortly after its completion in 1963. Also includes a commemorative United States Postal Service stamp made from Ezra Stoller's photograph.</p>  
